text: Cecilia Cenci (3 August 1942 - 21 September 2014) was an Argentine actress. She was best known her roles in the movies Piedra libre (1976) and Contragolpe (1979). Cenci was born in La Plata, Buenos Aires Province. She was of Italian ancestry. Cenci died from brain cancer on 21 September 2014 at the Fundaci√≥n Favaloro in Buenos Aires.
